{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-programs-js","path":"/programs/submission.html","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>The Submission page enables you to set specific requirements for hackers to submit reports to your program. You can require hackers to meet certain <a href=\"signal-requirements.html\">signal requirements</a> and set up two-factor authentication.</p>\n<h3 id=\"requiring-two-factor-authentication\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#requiring-two-factor-authentication\" aria-label=\"requiring two factor authentication permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Requiring Two-Factor Authentication</h3>\n<p>To require hackers to have two-factor authentication enabled before submitting reports to your program:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <b>Program Settings > Program > Submission</b>.</li>\n<li>Go to the section on requiring hackers to have 2FA.</li>\n<li>Click the toggle so that it's set to <b>Yes</b>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAXklEQVQI11WMMQ6AMAwD+/8H8AP+wcrGzMyCVNpGqGkpQqYZEsFwimNbdqUUCLXW31WY2dAs52xd7rrhwb3uOMcZLsaIEAKICKJTSob8X8STriLe4T2uPtiWDTRMeAG+l5igeXuJiQAAAABJRU5ErkJggg=='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"submission\"\n        title=\"submission\"\n        src=\"/static/e4ed72f251bb21683626e864b2be1ae7/0b533/submission-2a.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/e4ed72f251bb21683626e864b2be1ae7/fac75/submission-2a.png 125w,\n/static/e4ed72f251bb21683626e864b2be1ae7/63868/submission-2a.png 250w,\n/static/e4ed72f251bb21683626e864b2be1ae7/0b533/submission-2a.png 500w,\n/static/e4ed72f251bb21683626e864b2be1ae7/1d69c/submission-2a.png 750w,\n/static/e4ed72f251bb21683626e864b2be1ae7/00d43/submission-2a.png 1000w,\n/static/e4ed72f251bb21683626e864b2be1ae7/2eb79/submission-2a.png 1256w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<p>Hackers that have already submitted past reports before 2FA was required will still be able to access and comment on those reports. They, however, won't be able to submit any new reports to your program without enabling 2FA.</p>\n<h3 id=\"enabling-bounty-splitting\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#enabling-bounty-splitting\" aria-label=\"enabling bounty splitting permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Enabling Bounty Splitting</h3>\n<p><a href=\"/hackers/payments.html#bounty-splitting\">Bounty splitting</a> enables hackers to split the bounty with other hackers that helped collaborate on a report. This enables each hacker to be rewarded for their findings on the report.  </p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><strong>Note:</strong> You can only enable bounty splitting if your program uses the <a href=\"billing.html\">prepayment</a> billing option.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>To enable bounty splitting for your program:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Go to <b>Program Settings > Program > Submission</b>.</li>\n<li>Click the toggle so that it's set to <b>Yes</b> for <b>Enable bounty splitting</b>.</li>\n</ol>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 500px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 8.8%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAACCAYAAABYBvyLAAAACXBIWXMAABYlAAAWJQFJUiTwAAAAXElEQVQI141MSQqAMBDz+T7Jm+/w6K2FDtMFZwp1jLagZwMhCyGT9x4hBBARnHNgZpjZf7YTHbpuiPOCKcaIlBJyzui+lAJVRa11aKeIfL73bx4bUVzPofGBthNu0pSad1MXs2UAAAAASUVORK5CYII='); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"enable bounty splitting\"\n        title=\"enable bounty splitting\"\n        src=\"/static/934313c073ff0ef0227a8acb5956c5ff/0b533/enable-bounty-splitting.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/934313c073ff0ef0227a8acb5956c5ff/fac75/enable-bounty-splitting.png 125w,\n/static/934313c073ff0ef0227a8acb5956c5ff/63868/enable-bounty-splitting.png 250w,\n/static/934313c073ff0ef0227a8acb5956c5ff/0b533/enable-bounty-splitting.png 500w,\n/static/934313c073ff0ef0227a8acb5956c5ff/1d69c/enable-bounty-splitting.png 750w,\n/static/934313c073ff0ef0227a8acb5956c5ff/00d43/enable-bounty-splitting.png 1000w,\n/static/934313c073ff0ef0227a8acb5956c5ff/afa26/enable-bounty-splitting.png 1258w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>","frontmatter":{"path":"/programs/submission.html","id":"programs/submission","title":"Submission","description":null},"headings":[{"value":"Requiring Two-Factor Authentication"},{"value":"Enabling Bounty Splitting"}]}},"pageContext":{}},"staticQueryHashes":[]}